Package jetbrains.mps.util

Interface MacroHelper.Source

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MacrosFactory
    Enclosing interface:
    MacroHelper
    public static interface MacroHelper.Source
    PROVISIONAL API Source capable of producing MacroHelper instances. XXX need to decide whether this source has to be generic or have specific methods for typical usage scenarios (like module, etc). In latter case, would be nice to have a dedicated method for project. OTOH, it's unlikely we can specify all possible usage scenarions, and former approach, then, is more appealing (specific Source, e.g. the one aware of module files and their locations) would get instantiated where appropriate.

    Implementation note. Implementors of this interface that have no idea how to support specific methods are free to return more general instance, usually global one.

    Since:
    2018.1
